title: Become The Dream You
itunes:title: Become The Dream You
description:
Episode 504 - Who is it that you want to be in 10 years? What does that person look like? What are their habits? Who do they hang out with? These are all important questions that you need to answer in order to become the person that you want to be. In this episode, I dive into how to grow into the person in your dreams!
